Green Turf Landscaping

Our Service Area

Green Turf Landscaping, located in Lara, Hoppers Crossing, and Geelong, is dedicated to providing top-tier landscaping services to transform your outdoor spaces. Our expert team offers a wide range of services, including innovative landscaping design and installation, sturdy and attractive retaining walls, and high-quality synthetic grass installation for hassle-free lawns. We also provide Bobcat and Dingo hire for various landscaping and construction needs, professional earth-moving services to prepare your site, and safe, efficient tree removal to keep your property pristine. At Green Turf Landscaping, we combine expertise, quality materials, and exceptional service to deliver beautiful and functional outdoor environments.
